 | archivedate = 2011-08-21
}}</ref> и {{lang-en2|Current Affairs}}; национальный аудиоархив<ref name="md18">
{{cite web
 | url         = http://www.soundarchives.co.nz
 | title       = New Zealand Sound Archive
 | publisher   = New Zealand Sound Archive
 | accessdate  = 2009-04-21
